	(186,'Correction fluid (typewriter) and white out','Carpet','<li>Rubbing alcohol</li>','<li>Try rubbing alcohol on the stained area. To test       on the item in a non-visible area before using rubbing alcohol and clean       cloth. </li>\n  <li>The stain will begin to loosen. Test by touching the stain. Small flecks  of the white out should begin to come loose. Rinse thoroughly.</li>','<div class=\"boxChem\"><h3>Chemical solvents and supplies</h3><ul><li>Rubbing alcohol</li></ul></div><ol>\n  <li>Try rubbing alcohol on the stained area. To test       on the item in a non-visible area before using rubbing alcohol and clean       cloth. </li>\n  <li>The stain will begin to loosen. Test by touching the stain. Small flecks  of the white out should begin to come loose. Rinse thoroughly.</li>\n</ol>\n				\n				<h3>Steps to Clean</h3>\n				<ol>\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n				</ol>','107.jpg');
