	(188,'Rust','Washable Fabrics','<li>Nonprecipitating water softener</li>','<li>Do not use chlorine bleach on rust stain or in water containing large amounts of iron.</li>\n  <li>For a rusty water problem, use a nonprecipitating water softener, such as Calgon or Spring Rain, in both wash and rinse water.</li>\n  <li>For severe problems, install an iron filter in the water system.</li>','<h3>Steps to Clean</h3>\n				 <div class=\"boxChem\"><h3>Chemical solvents and supplies</h3><ul><li>Nonprecipitating water softener</li></ul></div><ol>\n  <li>Do not use chlorine bleach on rust stain or in water containing large amounts of iron.</li>\n  <li>For a rusty water problem, use a nonprecipitating water softener, such as Calgon or Spring Rain, in both wash and rinse water.</li>\n  <li>For severe problems, install an iron filter in the water system.</li>\n</ol>','166.jpg');
