s the stain.  Do not exceed 160 degrees Fahrenheit water with any synthetic fabrics*.  Launder.</li>\n  </ol>\n  <p>*<strong>Synthetic Fabrics</strong> are: Acetate, Acrylic, Polyester, Nylon, Olefin, Triacetate  and anything labeled static-resistant, wrinkle-resistant, permanent-press,  no-iron, stain-proof or moth-repellent</p>','69.jpg');
