tergent/vinegar       solution.</li>\n    <li>Blot until the liquid is absorbed.</li>\n    <li>Repeat Steps 6 and 7 until the stain disappears       or is no longer absorbed into the cloth. </li>\n    <li>Sponge the stain with rubbing alcohol.</li>\n    <li>Blot until the liquid is absorbed.</li>\n    <li>Sponge with cold water and blot dry</li>\n  </ol>','224.jpg');
